room_title: Escape room "Redemption" by Locked Up: Ocean Springs in Biloxi
room_description: You will be blindfolded and handcuffed. This room is not for the weak at heart! The Dark Angel wants you to repent for your sins. You must solve his twisted games to gain redemption and live to see another day. Do you have what it takes to play his game and earn your freedom? This is one of our more challenging rooms. It is multiple rooms with lots to solve!
